        <b>How to improve your tags with AI:</b>\n\n
        1. <b>Export:</b> Tap Export to save your tags as CSV\n\n
        2. <b>Share to LLM:</b> Share the CSV file with your favorite AI assistant (ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, etc.)\n\n
        3. <b>Get Improvements:</b> The CSV includes a prompt to help the AI suggest better tags, relationships, and new ideas\n\n
        4. <b>Import:</b> Copy the improved CSV from the AI and import it back using the Import option\n\n
        <b>Tip:</b> You can also manually edit the CSV file before importing!
